summary: headcanon: even though he’s super protective of his friends and acts like the mom friend, cyrus doesn’t really like or want...
body:
headcanon: even though he’s super protective of his friends and acts like the mom friend, cyrus doesn’t really like or want kids. tj, as it turns out, also doesn’t want kids because he thinks it’ll hurt too much when they grow up and leave him. so tj gets a job working with young kids with mental disabilities. that way, he can always have little kids around him, and cyrus doesn’t.

bonus: cyrus packs tj’s lunch for school every day and leaves a little note for him.

double bonus: cyrus does come in to visit from time to time, and he has to admit, they are pretty cute.
